# 统一换行符，避免跨平台（Windows/macOS/Linux）的 CRLF/LF 差异
# 落地 charles-coding skill 的"行尾统一 LF"约定

# 所有文本文件提交时一律转 LF
* text=auto eol=lf

# Windows 专用脚本保留 CRLF
*.bat  text eol=crlf
*.cmd  text eol=crlf
*.ps1  text eol=crlf

# 明确二进制文件，避免被当文本处理 / 换行符转换
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.webp binary
*.pdf  binary
*.zip  binary
*.gz   binary
*.jar  binary
*.war  binary
*.class binary
*.so   binary
*.dll  binary
*.exe  binary
